Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:53.57,OP,,0,0,0,,YO HO 轉換方向 左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.88,OP,,0,0,0,,YO HO 往左往右 瀟灑的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:09.84,OP,,0,0,0,,日落的時候 是出航宴會之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:22.52,OP,,0,0,0,,一點也不寂寞 只要活著一定會在哪再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:26.92,OP,,0,0,0,,迎面的風吹在臉上開始啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:31.50,OP,,0,0,0,,眼淚 眼淚 在流乾以前 是男人就該變強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:36.47,OP,,0,0,0,,友人啊 友人啊 總有一天 會笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:41.08,OP,,0,0,0,,堅強的 堅強的 這份羈絆 像互相認同的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:49.18,OP,,0,0,0,,現在這閃耀著光輝的未來的地圖 快把它緊緊抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:36.31,ED,,0,0,0,,笑著說我們是志同道合的同伴的那一時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:46.04,ED,,0,0,0,,小小的謊言也是能被寬恕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:52.72,ED,,0,0,0,,如果失去了二人可以回歸的場所 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:23:00.08,ED,,0,0,0,,因為我守護了那個笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:04.32,ED,,0,0,0,,多如繁星的聚會與別離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.71,ED,,0,0,0,,不想失去的東西全部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:11.27,ED,,0,0,0,,現在已經什麼都不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:16.64,ED,,0,0,0,,只想在你身邊凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:22.02,ED,,0,0,0,,快樂也好悲傷也罷 全部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:24.66,ED,,0,0,0,,現在開始從何處開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:27.22,ED,,0,0,0,,開始我們兩人的明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:31.62,ED,,0,0,0,,保持與生俱來的心境就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:36.99,ED,,0,0,0,,夏風輕搖 像花一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:45.87,ED,,0,0,0,,以這一瞬的綻放為傲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 電視機前的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,收看妖精的尾巴的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,請保持房間明亮 遠離電視
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精的尾巴 到上回為止是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,由拉格薩斯發動的妖精的尾巴之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雷神眾的艾芭把被艾爾莎打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,終於讓石化的我們復原了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在認為遊戲終了的時候拉格薩斯發動神鳴殿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,整個鎮上的人都成了人質
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好戲現在才要開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 是全身發光的獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你說過沒用的 攻擊靈魂是無效的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不管再怎麼破壞 我還是會附在新的人偶上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧 新的寶貝們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不管來幾個我都不會讓它們接近露西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕喲 玩COSPLAY的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,都說不是了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,露西 用盡全力上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,畢可斯羅本身並不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 只好使出那招了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,造型眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.33,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,figure eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,千萬別看他眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,雷神眾裡每個人的眼睛都有第二種魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不過艾芭是以它為主的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看到畢可斯羅的眼睛可是會變成人偶 靈魂會被他操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,閉上眼睛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,呀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆都不能睜開眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 沒有人能贏的過著附身人偶和造型眼的聯合攻勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,露西 暫時讓我回到門後 讓霍洛洛基姆來防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是你自己突然跑出來的 你又在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,鑰匙已經被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我相信你 所以你想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,碰碰運氣看了 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等我給你暗號 你就睜開眼睛衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 睜開眼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信我的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,充滿王之光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,獅子光耀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:15.80,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,lion flare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛 我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,洛基 你怎麼可能贏得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不是過去的那個我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到露西後 星靈原本的力量復甦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是遇到露西後 我變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和你操縱的人偶不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,愛讓星靈更加強大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,獅子王的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:49.62,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,regules impact
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你們真有一腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,別用奇怪的方式說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因為使用了兩名黃道十二門的星靈的緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,無論何時 我都會前來拯救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 露西贏了 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那個拉拉隊員贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,露西很強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人吧 因為她是拉拉隊員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是小露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拉拉隊員也很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,難道沒聽過拉拉隊員和烏龜的故事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是拉拉隊 是兔子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還是兔子輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 僅僅最初的一回比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只要解決這個問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是後來他們比了好幾百回是兔子贏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,改寫術式的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,原 原來如此 它學到了教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這是最難的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 用不同的速度解讀兩種文法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,經過一輪之後再用吉爾文法改變成同期文字整數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,再轉換成簡式文字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,先等等 我去改寫術式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,納茲 伽吉爾 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要加入妖精的尾巴之戰了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我燃起來了 去大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,艾爾夫曼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好嚴重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 你復原了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 艾爾夫曼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼姐姐你要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管是上次對幽鬼 還是這次 都無能為力 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用做什麼的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等到這場無聊的打架結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你再用笑容來迎接大家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 姐姐 不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,九碧雅 離神鳴殿發動還有多久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想還有三十分左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格薩斯那傢伙 什麼妖精的尾巴之戰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,自己還不是躲起來什麼事不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格薩斯在保留魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他真的打算和會長一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 現在要保留實力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個人設下了術式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,想逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 是術式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,規則 直到有一方無法戰鬥為止 禁止離開這個術式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我會和勝者交手 那麼開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了 弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想一對一 用不著這樣 我來對付你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,放我們離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還是你怕我們兩個同時對付你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,居然害怕兩個女人 你也太丟臉了吧 弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想盡力減少死在我手下的人數而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:08:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,讓同伴如此自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望最好留下的是卡娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,九碧雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你也是幽鬼的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道你會不會背叛妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里德 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,既然這樣 那也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,九碧雅 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的能在我們其中之一倒下後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,堂堂正正地與剩下的人對決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕不會破壞規則
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是來真的嗎 九碧雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就正中那傢伙的計了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你升多高 都不可能飛出術式的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果非要傷害誰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要傷害同伴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,衝向魔水晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,難道要攻擊它？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,九碧雅選擇這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,九碧雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,九碧雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣…術式就…解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,九碧雅 希望…儘快得到認可…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,認同我是妖精的尾巴的同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡大家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說些什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們早就已經是同伴了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還說什麼認可不認可的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,本來就已經是同伴了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個了不起的妖精的尾巴的魔導士啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,卡娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我好開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,九碧雅！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為…為什麼這個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,比起讓自己生存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,寧可選擇讓同伴活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里德！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,找不出拉格薩斯的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了？納茲 伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是掉進弗里德的術式陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那就一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡出去之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要分頭行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天我一定會找火龍一雪前恥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,首先打倒那個傲慢的打雷大哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他狠狠地修理過我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬會長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,伽吉魯 現在最重要的是取得同伴的信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要以妖精的尾巴一員的身份展開行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就已經在這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對妖精的尾巴的「懲罰」還在後頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人能走的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我…什麼都沒辦法做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,至少讓我稍微幫你的忙吧… 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼基本的東西都沒明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你有多強的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒擊中對手的話就毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,卡片魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂 死神 高山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,招雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗文字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…卡娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真耐打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是公會裡的元老
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,收回你說過的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,給我收回"九碧雅是幽鬼的女人"這句話！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,卡娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！到底發生了什麼事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！弗里德！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,混帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,艾爾夫曼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經輸給了艾芭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒有再回到遊戲的資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你適可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是同伴嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 在這個變換結構的遊戲裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那個概念已經被粉碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格薩斯的敵人 就是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,說那麼多廢話真煩人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,已經落敗的棋子禁止再度回到遊戲中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,破壞這個規則的人必須受到比死更嚴酷的拷問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗文字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這些字將會成為現實 成為你真實的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,艾爾夫曼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！弗里德！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,艾爾夫曼已經不能再戰鬥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗文字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了！你要我做什麼都可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,救救他！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,痛！痛！痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗文字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,死滅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,死？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧 艾爾夫曼哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,莉薩娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,身體動不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說話！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉姐 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 其實呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,莉薩娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,莉薩娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,莉薩娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 這種魔力是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉珍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗文字 翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這 這是魔人米拉珍的接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.18,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,satan soul
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗湧動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.01,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,darkness stream
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是禁止使用的招數但是沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,以魔制魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗文字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,暗黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.49,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,魔鬼閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.00,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,evil spark
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這 這是什麼樣的魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然聽過傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這真的是 那個米拉珍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我不能失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,暗黑氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.19,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,darkness breath
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,暗黑光彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.06,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,darkness flare bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,讓河水環繞在她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她到底有多強的魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,魔鬼爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.42,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,evil explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,靈魂滅絕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.75,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,soul extinction
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不可能會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是魔人真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這場戰鬥是無意義的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是勝者的傲慢嗎 米拉珍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,同一公會的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一同歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一同胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一同前行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我的同伴只有拉格薩斯一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不光他一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里德 其實你早注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:21:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然完仰賴一個人並不一定全是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你身邊還有很多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,人與人不論何時總是緊密相連的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 只要你伸出手來 我們就在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,當覺察到獨自一人 寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,人就能變得溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你發覺到了這一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事 我不想做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等到明年的這個時候 讓我們盡情的享受收穫祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
